data.description: Like new bi-attached home located on a private cul-de-sac in the heart of the rapidly growing city of Grimes. Close proximity to various amenities, including shopping, restaurants, and both Grimes Sports Complexes.  This well-maintained home offers a perfect blend of modern design and functionality. With a spacious layout and ample natural light, this property provides a comfortable and inviting atmosphere. Interior features a well-appointed kitchen with high-end appliances (all included), Quartz countertops, fireplace and plenty of storage space throughout. The home includes 2-beds and 2-baths on the main floor and spacious bedroom/full bath in the finished basement. Reach out today to schedule a showing for this move in ready home!
